<D>__{i think i can find my way now...}
<A>__{mark smiles.}
<C>__{inspector}
<D>__{...thanks for the escort}
<A>__{the inspector hurries towards the door of the set. the constable opens it and the inspector goes inside. the constable closes the door and stands in front of it. mark turns away quickly.}
